<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Since then, another bidder =E2=80=94=C2=A0a gr=
oup of hedge fund managers led by Boaz Weinstein and also including Bill Ac=
kman, Marc Lasry and <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/cli=
ck/32547544.257429/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbGVzLzIw=
MjMtMDgtMjEvc3VzcXVlaGFubmEtcy15YXNzLWpvaW5lZC13ZWluc3RlaW4tYWNrbWFuLWluLWJ=
pZC1mb3Itc2N1bHB0b3I_Y21waWQ9QkJEMDgyOTIzX01PTkVZU1RVRkYmdXRtX21lZGl1bT1lbW=
FpbCZ1dG1fc291cmNlPW5ld3NsZXR0ZXImdXRtX3Rlcm09MjMwODI5JnV0bV9jYW1wYWlnbj1tb=
