urned them down, arguing that they don=E2=80=99t really have financing and =
that their deal is too uncertain. The Weinstein group argues that they can=
=E2=80=99t make a fully committed offering if Sculptor won=E2=80=99t engage=
 with them, and that Sculptor=E2=80=99s board has brushed them off =E2=80=
