The ETF wants to be unlevered, so it will raise $100 from investors, put $3=
0 in the collateral account, and keep the other $70 in cash or whatever. We=
 discussed these mechanics <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.c=
om/click/32547544.257429/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydG=
