<div id=3D"footnote-2" class=3D"footnote-content" style=3D"font-style: ital=
ic;">
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">[2] To be clear, Bitcoin futures trade in lots=
 of places, including crypto exchanges that are not really regulated by any=
one, but the US-approved Bitcoin futures ETFs use futures traded on US regu=
lated exchanges.</p>
</div>
